"    </a>",
"    )",
"   </p>",
"   <div class=\"list ubnlist drugH1Div drugBrandNames\" id=\"F219144\" xmlns=\"file://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">",
"    <span class=\"drugH1\">",
"     Brand Names: U.S.",
"    </span>",
